1. link this dir to home.
2. then in autostart, you can include conky invocation using config files for
stats and clock.
3. the screensaver conky can be used with xscreensaver. edit ~/.xscreensaver
and include the following under the "programs" section.

                "Conky" conky -q --window-id=$XSCREENSAVER_WINDOW \
                -c ~/.conky/conkyrc-screensaver \n\

